\c 111 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 111\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Hojiin Waaqayyoo Inni Dinqisiisaan Bara Baraan Yaadatamuu
\m \bd 1\bd* Waaqayyoon jajadhaa! Walga'ii gara-qajeelotaa keessatti, waldicha keessattis Waaqayyoon garaa guutuudhaan nan galateeffadha!
\m \bd 2\bd* Wanti Waaqayyo hojjete hundinuu guddaa dha, warra itti gammadan hundumaaf kan qoramee bira ga'amee dha.
\m \bd 3\bd* Gochaan isaa surra-qabeessaa fi miidhagaa dha, qajeelummaan isaas yeroo hundumaaf jabaatee in dhaabata.
\m \bd 4\bd* Hojiin isaa inni dinqisiisaan akka yaadatamu godhe, Waaqayyo araara-qabeessa, oo'a-qabeessas.
\m \bd 5\bd* Inni warra isa sodaataniif soora in kennaaf, kakuu isaas bara baraan in yaadata.
\m \bd 6\bd* Wanta dhuunfaa saba lafa irraa ta'e isaaniif kennuudhaan, hojii aangoo isaa namoota isaatti mul'iseera.
\m \bd 7\bd* Hojiin harka isaa hundinuu amanamaa dha, dhugaa dha, abboommiin isaa hundinuus amansiisaa dha;
\m \bd 8\bd* isaan amanamummaa fi qajeelummaadhaan hojjetaman, yeroo hundumaaf baruma baraan jabaatanii in dhaabatu.
\m \bd 9\bd* Inni furii saba isaatiif erge, kakuun isaa bara baraan akka eegamu abboomeera, maqaan isaa immoo qulqulluu dha, sodaachisaa dhas!
\m \bd 10\bd* Waaqayyoon sodaachuun jalqaba ogummaa ti, warri isa duukaa bu'anii hojjetan hubannaa gaarii qabu; Waaqayyoon jajachuunis yeroo hundumaaf jabaatee in dhaabata.
\b 
